window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Eli Grayson is back. Life has been good to him since saving the elven princess and uncovering his powers as a Royal Blood.</p> <p>That is, until an army of the dead rises and threatens the fragile peace they'd achieved. As if that wasn’t enough to deal with, the ruling magical council has learned of his existence and wants to haul him in for judgement.</p> <p>Together with bond mates both new and old, he quickly finds himself on a magical realm-hopping adventure to uncover the source of the undead and win over the council.</p>"; 
